  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431220/extras/997497a3aafc34351e16f8012ef0b86d.webp?t=1602851366\" width=250 height=54 /></span><br><br><strong>10mg</strong> is a collection of 10 minute long games.<br><br><strong>SLASHER, Interrupted</strong> is a visual novel, in which you attempt to tell a horror story whilst your friends interrupt with their own ideas. Will you stick to a cohesive plot, or try and please everyone's ideas at once?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431220/extras/d7c9289a79a4ed11ade94a59b9387769.webp?t=1602851366\" width=396 height=56 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 7,000 words of lighthearted campfire banter<br></li><li> A branching story with 27 ending combinations<br></li><li> Pet a cat!<br></li><li> Kill multiple characters!<br></li><li> Get roasted for your messy plot choices!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431220/extras/997497a3aafc34351e16f8012ef0b86d.webp?t=1602851366\" width=250 height=54 /></span><br><br><strong>10mg</strong> is a collection of 10 minute long games.<br><br><strong>SLASHER, Interrupted</strong> is a visual novel, in which you attempt to tell a horror story whilst your friends interrupt with their own ideas. Will you stick to a cohesive plot, or try and please everyone's ideas at once?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431220/extras/d7c9289a79a4ed11ade94a59b9387769.webp?t=1602851366\" width=396 height=56 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 7,000 words of lighthearted campfire banter<br></li><li> A branching story with 27 ending combinations<br></li><li> Pet a cat!<br></li><li> Kill multiple characters!<br></li><li> Get roasted for your messy plot choices!</li></ul>",
